## Inheritance

[ref](http://rubylearning.com/satishtalim/ruby_inheritance.html)

* A class can only inherit from a *SINGLE* other class.


```ruby
class Mammal  
  def breathe  
    puts "inhale and exhale"  
  end  
end  
class Cat < Mammal  
  def speak  
    puts "Meow"  
  end  
end  
rani = Cat.new  
rani.breathe  
rani.speak 
```

